CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: I want to do this.

CONTENT: もう一つ ありました

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: that I want to do.

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Has President Miorine come out of her room yet?

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: She's...

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: I'll arrange for an option unit from Burion. Thank you! You're welcome.

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Do you think I'll let you see her?

CONTENT: ミオリネさんと まっすぐ。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: With Ms. Miorine. Heart to heart.

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Fix release!

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Follow me. Th...

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: I'll meet with Ericht and talk to my mom one more time.

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: But I've relied on Mom and Ericht for everything, all this time.

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: así que tomar una decisión sola me asusta mucho.

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: I can't. Ms. Miorine?

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: You have to decide on your own.

CONTENT: 全部
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: It was all...

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: a mistake.

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: I've made mistakes, too.

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: I told myself it was for everyone's protection...

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: that it was the right thing to do...

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: Pero cuando la escuela lo estaba pasando mal
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: But... when the school was in trouble,

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: y trabajamos juntos para restaurarla, estuve pensando.
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: and we were desperately doing recovery work... I realized something.

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Whether it was right or wrong,

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: Lo que has hecho no puede cambiarse.
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: what I've done can't be taken back.

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Even if there's nothing to gain, I have to move forward.

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: I don't want to... make any more mistakes.

CONTENT: 私が ここまで来れたのは

CONTENT: ミオリネさんと出会えたからです。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: because I met you, Ms. Miorine.

CONTENT: これは 間違いなんかじゃありません。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Nothing about that was a mistake.

CONTENT: いつか
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Someday...

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: come with me... to Earth.

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: I'm not strong enough to face what I've done by myself.

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: Pero no puedo fingir que no ha pasado.
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: But I can't turn away from it, either.

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: May I... open the door?

CONTENT: ⚟ダメ。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: No.

CONTENT: 自分で行く。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: I'll go on my own.

CONTENT: 自分で開ける。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: I'll open it myself.

CONTENT: D指数 90を突破。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: The D-index has exceeded 90.

CONTENT: 復旧終了。全システム 再稼働。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Recovery complete. All systems reactivated.

CONTENT: 目標　プラント・クエタ。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: Nuestro objetivo es la planta Quetta.
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Our objective is... Plant Quetta.

CONTENT: ごめん みんな。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: I'm sorry, everyone.

CONTENT: お前のために来たわけじゃねぇ。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: We didn't come here for you.

CONTENT: 行けよ。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Go on.

CONTENT: おやじ 目ぇ覚ましたんだろ。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Your father woke up, didn't he?

CONTENT: うん。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Right...

CONTENT: まだ 声を出すのは難しい状況です。

CONTENT: 私 逃げないから。会社も ガンダムの呪いからも。

CONTENT: だから あんたも 諦めて死ぬんじゃないわよ　クソおやじ!

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: So I won't allow you to give up and die, either! You lousy father!

CONTENT: やはり 先手を打たれたようです。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: They seem to have beaten us to it.

CONTENT: なら こちらから伺おうかしら
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: En ese caso, le haremos una visita...
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: In that case, let's pay a visit....

CONTENT: デリング・レンブランのところへ。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: to Delling Rembran himself.

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: Índice de despliegue de la tormenta de datos de Quiet Zero al 60 %.
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: At present, Quiet Zero's data storm deployment level is only at 60%.

CONTENT: プロスペラ・マーキュリーは ユニットを回収するために　プラント・クエタへ 向かうはずです。

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: That's why Prospera Mercury has to go to Plant Quetta to recover certain units.

CONTENT: もし あれが 完全な状態になれば...。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Once it's fully completed...

CONTENT: 地球圏全体を覆うほどの データストームを　展開できる... か。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: La tormenta de datos podrá cubrir todo el territorio de la Tierra.
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: It can deploy a data storm capable of covering the entire Earth Sphere, yes?

CONTENT: 本社フロント宙域に 防衛艦隊を配備済みですが...。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: Hay una flota defensiva en el frente de la empresa, pero...
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: We've stationed a defensive fleet around the head office front, but...

CONTENT: データストームの中で動けるのは ガンダムだけってことね。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: Solo los Gundams pueden moverse en la tormenta.
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: The only machines that can move in the data storm are Gundams, right?

CONTENT: 冗談 言うなよ。スコア8なんて浴びたら 即死だ。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: Ni pensarlo. La puntuación ocho es una muerte inmediata.
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: You've got to be kidding me. At score 8, you'll die instantly.

CONTENT: ファラクトは そもそも　高負荷のスコアに 耐えられる設計ではないんです。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: El Pharact no está programado para soportar una puntuación alta.
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: The Pharact was never designed to withstand such a high score load.

CONTENT: なら シュバルゼッテの仕様を 書き換えて使えば...。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: Si modificamos la configuración del Schwarzette...
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Can't we use the Schwarzette by rewriting its specifications?

CONTENT: 今からでは とても...。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: There's not enough time. Too late...

CONTENT: デミバーディングの オプションユニットに　スイッチ可能な コクピットスペースがあります。

CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: The Demi Barding's option unit has a switchable cockpit space.

CONTENT: パーメットリンクを介さない 操縦システムを載せれば...。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: Con un sistema de piloteo que no use enlace Permet...
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: If you add a control system that doesn't use Permet links...

CONTENT: オーバーライドされずに 稼働できる。
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: Podrá moverse sin que lo invalide.
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: ...you can operate it without being overridden.
